{"title":"养蚕谣","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"养蚕谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养蚕谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕眠人不眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕老人不闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蚕通身水晶般的亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送它上树心里最喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话儿细对蚕宝宝说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“赶天晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁热和，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织个茧儿像铁壳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游开做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各做各，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫让乱丝网你的脚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦秸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油菜棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯桠桠开出花万朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个新蚕一声笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一丈新丝一首歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声不断歌不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要唱得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六万万人穿绫罗！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青杠林子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柞蚕吃叶沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山满坡尽是青杠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青杠林接青杠林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连成了绿色的篷帐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妹子，小妹子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是什么地方？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这地方树子长青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩护过英雄儿郎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这地方梭镖如林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火曾照到大天光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志哥，同志哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是游击队的故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡里你来安家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随带着打鸟的猎枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守护着公社的山蚕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真像个战士在站岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕孃，蚕孃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是谁家的姑娘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是大巴山的女儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击队是我的爹娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红标语还刻在枪枝上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前人的话呀我不会忘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡，老乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要青杠像我，我像青杠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1961年5月四川南江"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}